{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Design a Tabbed Pricing Section for mobile repairs in Shopify.
    Create two tabs at the top:
    Hardware Repairs | Software Services
    Under the Hardware Repairs tab, display a clean pricing table with 3 columns:
    
    Service | Common Models | Starting Price (PKR)
    
    Add rows such as:
    
    Glass Replacement | Infinix Note 12, Spark 10 | Rs. 1,500 – 2,500
    
    Full Panel (Sunlong) | Samsung A32, A51, iPhone X | Rs. 4,500 – 15,000
    
    Battery Swap | All Android Models | Rs. 1,200 – 3,000
    
    Charging Jack | Universal | Rs. 500 – 1,000
    
    Table should look modern, easy to scan, and mobile-responsive with clear pricing transparency.
{% enddoc %}
